<br>
<B>Simbelmynë</B> : Very usefull to play all of your rohan possession (mount or weapon and your rohan caracter ( théoden or Hlafwine )<br>
Each Mount : for exerting minion at the start of the skirmish so you have more chance to kill them at the start of the skirmish so you can move a lot<br>
<br>
<B>Eomer + Eomer&#39;s spear + firefoot</B> => in a skirmish he is Damage + 2, defender +1 and has a strength of 11 (or more if he skirmish more than one minion with more than one wound )<br>
<br>
<B>Eowyn + eowyn sword</B>  => 9  and damage +1 ( if you have Hlafwine in play)<br>
<br>
<B>Théoden + King&#39;s mail + Rider&#39;s mount + herugrim</B> => can take a wound only in a skirmish phase and he is 8 , damage+1 and has 3 point of vitality <br>
<br>
<B>Aragorn + Horse of Rohan + Ranger&#39;s sword</B> => Defender+1 with a strength of 10 or 14<br>
<br>
You can also protect the bearer from 6 minion<br>
<br>
<B><U>Shadow Strategy :</U></B><br>
<br>
The shadow strategy is simple : <B>burdern, burden and a lot of burden</B><br>
<br>
<B>Step 1</B>: <U>add a lot of burden by using :</U><br>
New Fear<br>
Gathering to the Summons<br>
Vision From Afar (it&#39;s great if your opponent play succide)<br>
Easterling Lieutenant<br>
Easterling Guard<br>
<br>
<B>Step 2</B>: <U>use burden</U><br>
Attack with Easterling Trooper (who are 9 fierce damage+1 if you can spot 3 burden)<br>
Add twilight in the twilight pool with Easterling Skirmisher (+1 for each burden, limit 5)<br>
add strenght bonus to your troop with Easterling Captain<br>
<br>
<B>Step 3</B>: <U>if you have a lot of burden  (>= 6)</U><br>
Kill compagnion with Deser Legion (who are 18, fierce, damage+1 )<br>
<br>
<B>Step 4</B>: <U>win the game/U><br>
You have to choice for winning the game<br>
 -> Kill every one<br>
 -> Add ten burdens<br>
<br>
Sorry for the Desert Legion who are not easterling but they are too powerfull in a burden game<br>
